WEBVTT

00:02.936 --> 00:05.086
Hey, have you ever heard of
the Van Nuys Comic-Con?

00:05.110 --> 00:05.938
‭Yeah.

00:05.939 --> 00:08.473
It's a dinky little convention
where they sell collectibles

00:08.475 --> 00:11.560
and get sad D-list celebrities
to appear. Why?

00:11.562 --> 00:13.562
I got asked
to sign autographs there.

00:13.564 --> 00:15.981
That's awesome!

00:17.117 --> 00:18.533
Is this for
Serial Ape-ist?

00:18.535 --> 00:20.152
Well, it could be
for the monkey movie.

00:20.154 --> 00:21.820
It could be
my hemorrhoid commercial.

00:21.822 --> 00:23.121
The list does not go on.

00:23.903 --> 00:25.373
- When is it?
- It doesn't matter.

00:25.375 --> 00:25.985
I'm not doing it.

00:26.009 --> 00:27.376
What? Why not?

00:27.377 --> 00:28.877
You just said yourself,
it's sad.

00:28.879 --> 00:30.212
Yeah, but it's
not pathetic.

00:30.214 --> 00:32.080
That's where
I draw the line.

00:33.333 --> 00:34.716
Come on! We'll have fun.

00:34.718 --> 00:35.884
I don't know.

00:35.886 --> 00:37.969
You'll have nerds
fawning all over you.

00:37.971 --> 00:40.672
If you don't love that,
this marriage is in trouble.

00:40.674 --> 00:42.924
I guess it wouldn't hurt
to meet some fans

00:42.926 --> 00:44.426
and make a little extra money.

00:44.428 --> 00:45.894
Yeah.

00:45.896 --> 00:48.980
Wow! An appearance
by George Lucas...

00:48.982 --> 00:51.149
...'s dermatologist.

00:52.486 --> 00:55.020
- Oh, I want that autograph.
- Oh, yeah.

00:55.022 --> 00:58.657
